      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PADUCAH (4) has a strong record this track and trip with two wins and two placings from five starts. Placed last time (19.92) at this track in a Grade 6, finishing third and beaten 2.5 lengths. Looks a key chance on best form. CHEAT CODE (2) missed the frame last time when fifth (20.09) at this track but prior to that had four placings in a row. Solid record here winning three races. The form out of his last race has been franked. Will give the top chances plenty to think about. FEDERAL LADY (8) settled midfield in the run and boxed on to finish there when 4th (19.96) at this track. Some good form is emerging from her last run. In the mix. STORM SISTER (5) was a surprise last-start placegetter with solid claims again.",
